w日本最正啲梳，好多都唔係扁平嗰款，而係L型有齒嗰種，有啲仲要對摺得，勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前係paris酒店啲amenities係NUXE <br />\n叫佢拎多一set上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef0dd68a853b8202bef89f423500de5b59af77e","tid":486910,"uid":53575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"個個都拎毛巾摔過屎眼都拎？"},{"pid":"3ef82954789e8e98b7cb434329cba11900696b54","tid":486910,"uid":121240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T18:16:14.000Z","msg":"好少拎<br />\n但如果啲洗頭水沐浴露隻味我覺得香先會拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31088ccaa678ca3d38c1b7ab94733642b2b4b3f9","tid":486910,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T21:06:54.000Z","msg":"試過拎走電視"},{"pid":"91215f78a51217b20a7cd8a7c88b20c2610b7ce8","tid":486910,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T23:12:53.000Z","msg":"拎洗衫袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f302d13519aa66798feb37478237edf2388447","tid":486910,"uid":428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T23:19:16.000Z","msg":"筆"},{"pid":"f5241bda0dfd2cbf7fca15d6618dc10c88b6024f","tid":486910,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:04:14.000Z","msg":"如果係啲mini 裝嘅洗頭水/沐浴露用過覺得好就會攞走<br />\n<br />\n只限mini size, 如果係一大碌嘅送比我都唔要<br />\n其他野都唔會攞走<br />\n貪N手貨好正咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a1eea606e8bb4d7a65f7d9338c1c0b2d495a37","tid":486910,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T00:18:44.000Z","msg":"拎淋浴露走"},{"pid":"e9989ff63bc229a817b2d38b7a04c2d5e1b7bc6c","tid":486910,"uid":12827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"唔會拎任何野，會自己帶野去用<br />\n因為出差一年住差不多百幾2百日酒店，想用番慣用既野多d<br />\n自己最過份就係拎左人個酒桶去做公事用，但下次住果時比番佢<br />\n有相熟既酒店員工同我講，佢地最誇有人偷電視機......."},{"pid":"20c1d0bfc54b1885ae813986dff5876bcc275937","tid":486910,"uid":25097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去日本啲酒店好多都係一大支shampoo或者soap<br />\n想攞都攞唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去日本旅行都會帶定d細樽仔，然後裝d當地既洗頭水走<br />\n<br />\n唔係為咗貪佢洗頭水矜貴，而係耐唔耐攞返樽嘢出嚟，開樽聞下陣味，會瞬間諗返起當時旅行既開心日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會太變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>丨フ一一一丨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/223003_968b81a0f4c3859b79c1cf43c975cb11.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F223003_968b81a0f4c3859b79c1cf43c975cb11.JPG&h=c01d7a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近先拎完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw日本最正啲梳，好多都唔係扁平嗰款，而係L型有齒嗰種，有啲仲要對摺得，勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前係paris酒店啲amenities係NUXE <br />\n叫佢拎多一set上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前係巴黎住過間酒店係用Hermes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  拎哂黎屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dc4d50ec4db1a4bfedf1759bed068f0826fdaa","tid":486910,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都唔會拎 又無咩特別<br />\n但上次住迪士尼酒店 對拖鞋好軟幾舒服<br />\n仲寫住話給你的禮物 拎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n探索家酒店個盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n筆盒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬聖節同聖誕節都有</blockquote><br />\n係啊我係住探索家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔係萬聖節同聖誕節去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5048b6c8e38cbd8663b420c9a817c6977a893634","tid":486910,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都係帶牙刷牙膏同洗頭水走，唔帶走佢都係dum<br />\n<br />\n有時會攞衛生袋(好實淨，裝嘢好方便)同埋剃鬚刀，剃鬚刀多到而家唔需要再自己買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d好用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d通常都好易刮損，拎都費時</blockquote><br />\n視乎住邊間酒店啦，有d質素都可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算五星級 一樣垃圾<br />\n你重懶醒拎咁多😂"},{"pid":"d10903fc3a6fa0779c694f0934ba6c9e8e0c7b86","tid":486910,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/204114_9b324b6f257085bfbe601e5486167fa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F204114_9b324b6f257085bfbe601e5486167fa4.jpg&h=c5233221&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nKids?!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國人好能興😂"},{"pid":"78963f78cd494d96bf49528ffac7d1f36c554913","tid":486910,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都係帶牙刷牙膏同洗頭水走，唔帶走佢都係dum<br />\n<br />\n有時會攞衛生袋(好實淨，裝嘢好方便)同埋剃鬚刀，剃鬚刀多到而家唔需要再自己買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d好用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d通常都好易刮損，拎都費時</blockquote><br />\n視乎住邊間酒店啦，有d質素都可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算五星級 一樣垃圾<br />\n你重懶醒拎咁多😂</blockquote><br />\n剃得乾淨就得啦，廢時另外曬錢買"},{"pid":"320c57023727a0d18e88055e9e62baa86caa6bc3","tid":486910,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"之前浸溫泉有比紮辮橡筋，見幾好用就拎埋另一包走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好用過香港街邊檔，用極都唔會鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be460e4c50d6af326a8332207596f9955dc72cc","tid":486910,"uid":16940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去日本啲酒店好多都係一大支shampoo或者soap<br />\n想攞都攞唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去日本旅行都會帶定d細樽仔，然後裝d當地既洗頭水走<br />\n<br />\n唔係為咗貪佢洗頭水矜貴，而係耐唔耐攞返樽嘢出嚟，開樽聞下陣味，會瞬間諗返起當時旅行既開心日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會唔會太變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會</blockquote><br />\n我反而會拎啲沙走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7b1c8010178c17c71734ceb9d12b62376a3a85","tid":486910,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定會，啲passport身份證唔拎走過唔到關</blockquote><br />\n你確定? 會唔會冇拎走個腦?</blockquote><br />\n[edit]</blockquote><br />\n我以為個edit係掣嚟有得㩒</blockquote> <br />\n哇好撚好笑 <br />\n[按此取回智商]</blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d240a027bd9807c76e357be74b1da89b377881d6","tid":486910,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"成日拎果d洗衣袋，用黎裝污糟衫"},{"pid":"97c06a52c6142ecd2ca2acd4ce2602006627a331","tid":486910,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"試過住過一間日本酒店，<br />\n勁多DHC一包包既野，洗頭水、護髮素、沐浴露、Night Cream、防曬都有，<br />\n結果拎左勁多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f544510e77ff497deec272dcf82cd4c1ccfe507","tid":486910,"uid":370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番梘 拖鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著一次就掉左佢個心過意唔去。屋企有幾對</blockquote><br />\n公司個秘書會係office着酒店拖鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004b38c9e51e28e47146bcfeb07c61c6e5672afb","tid":486910,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>番梘 拖鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 著一次就掉左佢個心過意唔去。屋企有幾對</blockquote><br />\n公司個秘書會係office着酒店拖鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母拎拎埋埋幾袋 屋企已經唔大 仲要塞晒係度<br />\n牙刷都叫可以刷下野 但拖鞋佢係拎去人地屋企個時著<br />\n最後比我一次過dum晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}